"[{\"comment\": \"I know this is a salt thread and all but you can easily beat a jade druid with midrange decks  Just outpace them they have a very hard time getting the board back  If you play passively and let their jades grow its an autoloss\", \"commentId\": \"34580\", \"commentDate\": \"1491244165\"}, {\"comment\": \"I used to think I was good at everything  Then I played this game  I want to quit because Im tired of sucking\", \"commentId\": \"34581\", \"commentDate\": \"1491244782\"}, {\"comment\": \"I got a play 50 warlock cards quest  so Im using a demonKrul Renolock I made   I just lost my TWELFTH GAME AND I HAVE YET TO DRAW RENO ONCE  NOT ONCE   Needless to say Im 210 one win from an instaconcede   Ive check twice to make sure hes actually in the the deck he is   Ive completed the quest by the point  but jist have to keep going to see how long I can keep up this streak  Unbelievable  The other weird thing is in 1012 games Ive mulliganed my single copy of Shadowflame\", \"commentId\": \"34582\", \"commentDate\": \"1491244932\"}, {\"comment\": \"Noobs on autopiloting decks  Deck building No  We will go full face  play oncurve high heals minions and discover whatever need have infinitively growing minions  P s  and each exp  lets give to Priest only 4 mana minions gimmick spells useless legendaries no support for main theme  Why\", \"commentId\": \"34583\", \"commentDate\": \"1491245081\"}, {\"comment\": \"So as usual doing my quirky quests in Casual   had a Murloc quest and damn I faced 7 friggin Dragon Priests in  row and if that was not enough lets add a few Pirate Warriors for fun  seriously people   I would like a reply to your Happy New Year that says  Happy New year you Nutless Wonder\", \"commentId\": \"34584\", \"commentDate\": \"1491249922\"}, {\"comment\": \"Last 8 games have been shaman  That should say enough\", \"commentId\": \"34585\", \"commentDate\": \"1491252226\"}, {\"comment\": \"Yogg FUCK YOU AND THE CUNT THAT PLAYED YOU JUST STOLE A GAME THAT YOU HAD NO CHANCE OF WINNING\", \"commentId\": \"34586\", \"commentDate\": \"1491255499\"}, {\"comment\": \"Im not normally a salt thread type but my last 4 games of Maly Kun Druid were kind of absurd 1   Jade Druid Ramped like a madman and had 44 Jades by turn 4 with like 7 mana  topdecked Nourish to replenish his hand  drew exclusively bigger Jades and Fandral to power up every other card he played  Loss 2  Meme Shaman looked like a JadeYShaarjCrusher sort of list with Goya Game is going okay  a bit in his favor but Ive got most of my combo pieces and some draw in hand to close things rapidly  I mulch his Ysera  receive a Thank You  YShaarj comes down with the tag Created by Mulch  and he pulls a YShaarj from the deck  I see I can hold for another turn and set up to do so  I draw dead  Loss  3  Pirate Warrior  I dont draw earlygame  Loss  4  Renolock  Easy matchup  he doesnt apply pressure all game  I assemble my combo pieces other than Kun and start drawing toward the bottom of my deck  Kun is my last card  Next turn I have lethal  Dirty Rat pulls my Malygos the only card I 100 needed to secure the game out of six minions in my hand from hand  Twisting Nether  I all in on the board since its my only option  MC Tech steals my Alex  Defender of Argus creates a wall  I punch through  have lethal next turn  Blastcrystal Potion and Demonwrath clean me out  He still has like 10 cards in his deck  Im in fatigue with no cards in hand or on the board  Loss  I dont think Hearthstone wants to see me today  Part of the experience I guess  Ill have better days\", \"commentId\": \"34587\", \"commentDate\": \"1491255679\"}, {\"comment\": \"How close are we to finally getting some Pirate CuntFuck relief  Please tell me next week at the latest   I just want those fat taunts  Pirate killing minions  and whatever other overpowered shit they made to get rid of that loser ass shit   I hope the entire pirate archetype dies and never returns   You have to some kind of asshole to