alue  so everyone should craft them now if they dont already have them for free cards in Wild\", \"commentId\": \"34596\", \"commentDate\": \"1491267552\"}, {\"comment\": \"Mage is a complete RNG crap fast   Its so disgusting\", \"commentId\": \"34597\", \"commentDate\": \"1491279270\"}, {\"comment\": \"I hate variance  8 games in a row without Tunnel Trogg in my starting hand\", \"commentId\": \"34598\", \"commentDate\": \"1491289448\"}, {\"comment\": \"Was that common knowledge You are completely right  I did not expect this  I assumed it would stick on my side of the field  Because of that I ended up with a tougher game than it was before\", \"commentId\": \"34599\", \"commentDate\": \"1491289613\"}]"